1. Click OK.\n12. Click OK.\n    * Confirm the adjustment is proposed. The amount proposed is discounted to the present value.  \n13. Click Post.\n\n","nodes":[{"pos":[5,655],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"# required metadata \n \ntitle: Adjust an asset retirement obligation estimate (Japan)\ndescription: For Japan, the initial estimate of the asset retirement obligations (ARO) can be adjusted. \nauthor: ShylaThompson\nmanager: AnnBe \nms.date: 11/10/2016\nms.topic: business-process \nms.prod:  \nms.service: dynamics-ax-applications \nms.technology:  \n \n# optional metadata \n \n# ms.search.form:   \naudience: Application User \n# ms.devlang:  \nms.reviewer: shylaw\nms.search.scope: Operations \n# ms.tgt_pltfrm:  \n# ms.custom:  \nms.search.region: Japan\n# ms.search.industry: \nms.author: shylaw\nms.search.validFrom: 2016-06-30 \nms.dyn365.ops.version: Version 7.0.0 ","nodes":[{"content":"Adjust an asset retirement obligation estimate (Japan)","nodes":[{"pos":[0,54],"content":"Adjust an asset retirement obligation estimate (Japan)","nodes":[{"content":"Adjust an asset retirement obligation estimate (Japan)","pos":[0,54]}]}],"path":["title"],"extradata":"MT"},{"content":"For Japan, the initial estimate of the asset retirement obligations (ARO) can be adjusted.","nodes":[{"pos":[0,90],"content":"For Japan, the initial estimate of the asset retirement obligations (ARO) can be adjusted.","nodes":[{"content":"For Japan, the initial estimate of the asset retirement obligations (ARO) can be adjusted.","pos":[0,90]}]}],"path":["description"],"extradata":"MT"}],"header":"# required metadata \n","yml":true},{"pos":[662,716],"content":"Adjust an asset retirement obligation estimate (Japan)","linkify":"Adjust an asset retirement obligation estimate (Japan)","nodes":[{"content":"Adjust an asset retirement obligation estimate (Japan)","pos":[0,54]}]},{"content":"For Japan, the initial estimate of the asset retirement obligations (ARO) can be adjusted.","pos":[78